I gotta throw in that I don't smile when the tax man comes a calling, rather
I want Uncle Sam the heck out of my pocket book.  Frankly I can't see why I
should pay higher taxes  ( Yes, you're fooling yourself if you think you can
increase the size of the fed govt w/o them raising your taxes ) to destroy
the objects of my hobby, and much less the livelihood of people that restore
these classic vehicles and keep them running for a living.  The govt is
taking potential business away from them.

Bryant


